msgstr "Peaaken"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:122
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This section provides a quick tour of the main interface which is comprised "
"of the following areas:"
msgstr ""
"Käesolevas osas tutvustatakse lühidalt peaakent, mis koosneb järgmistest "
"osadest:"

