#: index.docbook:124
#, no-c-format
msgid "<para>Menus</para>"
msgstr "<para>Menüüd</para>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:125
#, no-c-format
msgid "<para>Toolbar</para>"
msgstr "<para>Tööriistariba</para>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:126
#, no-c-format
msgid "<para>Source and Destination Folders</para>"
msgstr "<para>Lähte- ja sihtkataloogid</para>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:127
#, no-c-format
msgid "<para>Source and Destination Files</para>"
msgstr "<para>Lähte- ja sihtfailid</para>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:128
#, no-c-format
msgid "<para>Source and Destination Line Changes</para>"
msgstr "<para>Lähte- ja sihtfaili ridade erinevused</para>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:129
#, no-c-format
msgid "Source and Destination Text View"
msgstr "Lähte- ja sihtfaili tekstivaade"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:130
#, no-c-format
msgid "<para>Statusbar</para>"
msgstr "<para>Olekuriba</para>"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:134
#, no-c-format
msgid "<title>Menus</title>"
msgstr "<title>Menüüd</title>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:135
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&kompare; provides a menu driven interface. Explanation to the menu items "
"and their options is provided in <xref linkend=\"command-reference\"/>."
msgstr ""
"&kompare; juhtimine käib menüüde abil. Menüükirjeid selgitab lähemalt <xref "
"linkend=\"command-reference\"/>."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:139
#, no-c-format
msgid "<title>Toolbar</title>"
msgstr "<title>Tööriistariba</title>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:140
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The &kompare; toolbar provides shortcuts to the most frequently used diff "
"and merge operations. The toolbar orientation, text positioning, icon size "
"properties and which shortcut icons are displayed can be customized from the "
"toolbar context menu accessed when right-clicking the toolbar with the "
"mouse. The toolbar context menu also enables the toolbar to be hidden. If "
"the toolbar is hidden and you wish to unhide it, select "
"<menuchoice><guimenu>Settings</guimenu><guimenuitem>Show Toolbar</"
"guimenuitem></menuchoice>."
msgstr ""
"&kompare; tööriistariba võimaldab kiiresti kasutada kõige levinumaid "
"võrdlemis- ja ühendamistoiminguid. Tööriistariba orientatsiooni, teksti "
"asetust, ikoonide suurust ja seda, milliseid ikoone kuvatakse, saab "
"kohandada tööriistariba kontekstimenüü abil, mis avaneb tööriistaribal hiire "
"parema nupuga klõpsates. Kontekstimenüü abil saab tööriistariba ka "
"täielikult peita. Kui see on peidetud ja sa soovid seda taas näha, vali "
"<menuchoice><guimenu>Seadistused</guimenu><guimenuitem>Tööriistariba "
"näitamine</guimenuitem></menuchoice>."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:147
#, no-c-format
msgid "<title>Source and Destination Folders</title>"
msgstr "<title>Lähte- ja sihtkataloogid</title>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:148
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The source folder and destination folder panes display the folders in which "
"compared files reside. When many subfolders are included in the comparison, "
"then selecting a folder will display the first document in that folder where "
"a difference was found between the source and destination."
msgstr ""
"Lähte- ja sihtkataloogi paneelil kuvatakse katalooge, milles asuvad "
"võrreldavad failid. Kui võrdlusse on kaasatud palju alamkatalooge, kuvatakse "
"kataloogi valimisel esimest selles asuvat dokumenti, mille puhul tuvastati "
"läthe- ja sihtfaili erinevusi."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:154
#, no-c-format
msgid "<title>Source and Destination Files</title>"
msgstr "<title>Lähte- ja sihtfailid</title>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:155
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The source and destination file pane displays files where a difference was "
"found for the currently selected source or destination folder. When a folder "
"has multiple documents containing differences, all documents with a "
"difference are listed. The selected document is displayed."
msgstr ""
"Lähte- ja sihtfaili paneelil kuvatakse faile, mille puhul tuvastati "
"erinevusi parajasti valitud lähte- või sihtkataloogis. Kui kataloogis on "
"hulga erinevusi sisaldavaid dokumente, lisatakse kõik need nimekirja. "
"Kuvatakse valitud dokumenti."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:160
#, no-c-format
msgid "<title>Source and Destination Line Changes</title>"
msgstr "<title>Lähte- ja sihtfaili ridade muudatused</title>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:161
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The source and destination line changes pane summarizes the differences "
"found between the current source and destination documents. Selecting a "
"record within the pane highlights and selects the difference. This is a "
"useful way to navigate and inspect long documents with many differences."
msgstr ""
"Lähte- ja sihtfaili ridade muudatuste paneelil kuvatakse lähte- ja sihtfaili "
"vahel tuvastatud erinevuste kokkuvõtet. Kirje valimine paneelil tõstab esile "
"ning valib erinevuse. See on abiks pikkades ja paljude erinevustega "
"dokumentides liikumisel."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:166
#, no-c-format
msgid "Source and Destination View"
msgstr "Lähte- ja sihtfaili vaade"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:167
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The source and destination view is the main workspace of &kompare;. The "
"contents and highlighted differences of the currently selected source and "
"destination file are displayed here with line numbers."
msgstr ""
"Lähte- ja sihtfaili vaade on &kompare; peamine tööala. Selles kuvatakse "
"valitud lähte- ja sihtfaili sisu ning esiletõstmisega erinevusi koos "
"reanumbritega."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:172
#, no-c-format
msgid "Text View"
msgstr "Tekstivaade"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:173
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The <guilabel>Text View</guilabel> is not displayed by default. It can be "
"opened by selecting <menuchoice><guimenu>Settings</guimenu><guimenuitem>Show "
"Text View</guimenuitem></menuchoice>."
msgstr ""
"<guilabel>Tekstivaadet</guilabel> vaikimisi ei kuvata. Selle saab avada "
"menüükäsuga <menuchoice><guimenu>Seadistused</"
"guimenu><guimenuitem>Tekstivaate näitamine</guimenuitem></menuchoice>."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:179
#, no-c-format
msgid "<title>Statusbar</title>"
msgstr "<title>Olekuriba</title>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:180
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The status bar provides a summary of the current source and destination file "
"or folder under comparison. The status bar also reports the number of "
"changes found in the current document and counts the differences that have "
"been applied. Furthermore, the status bar shows the overall number of "
"documents containing differences and the current document number selected "
"from this set. For example, a comparison run over two folders may return "
"1890 files with differences. The currently selected document is number 18 of "
"1890."
msgstr ""
"Olekuriba näitab parajasti võrreldavate lähte- ja sihtfailide või -"
"kataloogide kokkuvõtet. Samuti näeb seal aktiivses dokumendis leitud "
"muudatuste ning rakendatud erinevuste arvu. Lisaks näitab olekuriba valitud "
"dokumendikogumis erinevusi sisaldavate dokumentide koguarvu ning hetkel "
"võrreldava dokumendi järjekorranumbrit kogumis. Nii võib näiteks kahe "
"kataloogi võrdlemisel tekkida 1890 erinevusi sisaldavat faili ning aktiivne "
"dokument olla 18. dokument 1890-st."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:189
#, no-c-format
msgid "Viewing Differences"
msgstr "Erinevuste vaatamine"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:192
#, no-c-format
msgid "Managing Screen Real-Estate"
msgstr "Ekraanil kuvatavaga töötamine"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:193
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&kompare; displays the source and destination file under using equal "
"percentage of the main interface view work area. This view area provides "
"some features that help optimize use of screen real-estate while viewing "
"differences, including:"
msgstr ""
"&kompare; eraldab lähte- ja sihtfailile peaaknas ühepalju ruumi. Vaatealas "
"saab aga kasutada teatud vahendeid, mis aitavad paremini erinevusi uurida:"

#. Tag: term
#: index.docbook:197
#, no-c-format
msgid "Dual Scrollbars"
msgstr "Kaks kerimisriba"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:198
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The most obvious feature is that scrollbars are provided both on the right "
"and bottom edges of the view area. Using the scrollbars it is possible to "
"move rapidly through the comparison."
msgstr ""
"Kõige silmatorkavam võimalus on kerimisriba nii vaateala paremas servas kui "
"ka allservas. Kerimisribadega saab kiiresti dokumentides liikuda."

#. Tag: term
#: index.docbook:202
#, no-c-format
msgid "Share Grip Handle"
msgstr "Poolitav pide"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:203
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "The vertical space between the source and destination view not only makes "
#| "it possible to clearly see the start and end of lines in each of the "
#| "panes, but is also a grip handle that allows adjustment of percentage "
#| "occupied between the source and destinate views that comprise the view "
#| "pane. To change pane size for one of the views, hover the mouse pointer "
#| "over the grip handle then hold down the mouse button and drag left or "
#| "right. Naturally, increasing the area of one pane will decrease the area "
#| "available to the opposite pane within the view panel area."
msgid ""
"The vertical space between the source and destination view not only makes it "
"possible to clearly see the start and end of lines in each of the panes, but "
"is also a grip handle that allows adjustment of percentage occupied between "
"the source and destination views that comprise the view pane. To change pane "
"size for one of the views, hover the mouse pointer over the grip handle then "
"hold down the mouse button and drag left or right. Naturally, increasing the "
"area of one pane will decrease the area available to the opposite pane "
"within the view panel area."
msgstr ""
"Lähte- ja sihtfaili eraldav püstine riba lubab mõlemal poolel väga selgelt "
"näha ridade algust ja lõppu, kuid lisaks sellele saab seda ka liigutada ja "
"sel moel muuta lähte- või sihtfailile vaates antavat ruumi. Selleks vii "
"hiirekursor püstriba peale, klõpsa ja lohista seda vastavalt vajadusele "
"vasakule või paremale. Enesestmõistetavalt tähendab ühe poole suurendamine "
"teise poole vähenemist."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:207
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"A second horizontal handle is available between the navigation panel and the "
"source and destination view."
msgstr "Teine rõhtne pide asub liikumispaneeli ning lähte- ja sihtvaate vahel."

#. Tag: term
#: index.docbook:210
#, no-c-format
msgid "Docking"
msgstr "Dokkimine"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:212
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The navigation panel can be undocked from the main interface by clicking the "
"<inlinemediaobject> <imageobject><imagedata fileref=\"undock.png\" format="
"\"PNG\"/></imageobject></inlinemediaobject> icon located top right of the "
"panel. This opens it in a window of its own, allowing you to move it across "
"the screen. You can even hide the navigation panel by clicking the "
"<inlinemediaobject><imageobject><imagedata fileref=\"dock.png\" format=\"PNG"
"\"/></imageobject></inlinemediaobject> icon. To display a hidden navigation "
"bar again, click with the &RMB; into the menubar and select "
"<guilabel>Navigation</guilabel> from the context menu."
msgstr ""
"Liikumispaneeli võib pealiidesest eraldada, kui klõpsata paneeli ülemises "
"paremas nurgas asuvale ikoonile <inlinemediaobject> <imageobject><imagedata "
"fileref=\"undock.png\" format=\"PNG\"/></imageobject></inlinemediaobject>. "
"See muudab paneeli omaette aknaks ning võimaldab seda omatahtsi ekraanil "
"paigutada. Liikumispaneeli võib isegi peita, klõpsates ikoonile "
"<inlinemediaobject><imageobject><imagedata fileref=\"dock.png\" format=\"PNG"
"\"/></imageobject></inlinemediaobject>. Peidetud liikumispaneeli "
"taasnägemiseks klõpsa menüüribale &HPNga; ja vali kontekstimenüüst "
"<guilabel>Liikumine</guilabel>."

#. Tag: term
#: index.docbook:220
#, no-c-format
msgid "Statusbar Toggle"
msgstr "Olekuriba lülitamine"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:222
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The status bar of the view panel can be toggled on and off by selecting "
"<menuchoice><guimenu>Settings</guimenu><guimenuitem>Show Statusbar</"
"guimenuitem></menuchoice>."
msgstr ""
"Olekuriba näitamist saab sisse ja välja lülitada menüükäsuga "
"<menuchoice><guimenu>Seadistused</guimenu><guimenuitem>Olekuriba näitamine</"
"guimenuitem></menuchoice>."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:229
#, no-c-format
msgid "Switching Source and Destination Views"
msgstr "Lähte- ja sihtfaili vaate vahetamine"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:231
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "Sometimes it can be useful to consider what the file to which differences "
#| "where to be applied as the source. For example, when comparing two "
#| "modified versions of a file and discovering that the one file has many "
#| "more modifications that the other. The file with more changed would be "
#| "better as the source, since then fewer differences would need to be "
#| "applied."
msgid ""
"Sometimes it can be useful to consider what the file to which differences "
"where to be applied as the source. For example, when comparing two modified "
"versions of a file and discovering that one file has many more modifications "
"than the other. The file with more changes would be better as the source, "
"since then fewer differences would need to be applied."
msgstr ""
"Mõnikord on tulus kaaluda, milline fail võtta erinevuste vaatlemisel "
"võrdlemise aluseks, näiteks siis, kui faili kaht muudetud versiooni "
"võrreldes leiad, et ühes on muudatusi palju rohkem kui teises. Sel juhul "
"sobib paremini lähtefailiks rohkemate muudatustega fail, sest sel juhul on "
"vaja vähem erinevusi rakendada."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:234
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"In this case select <menuchoice><guimenu>File</guimenu><guimenuitem>Swap "
"Source with Destination</guimenuitem></menuchoice>. This will switch the "
"files displayed in all &kompare; panels."
msgstr ""
"Sel juhul vali menüükäsk <menuchoice><guimenu>Fail</"
"guimenu><guimenuitem>Vaheta lähtefail sihtfailiga</guimenuitem></"
"menuchoice>. See vahetab failid kõigis &kompare; paneelides."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:239
#, no-c-format
msgid "Displaying Difference Statistics"
msgstr "Erinevuste statistika kuvamine"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:240
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"For a quick overview of the differences, select <menuchoice><guimenu>File</"
"guimenu><guimenuitem>Show Statistics</guimenuitem></menuchoice>. This will "
"display the <guilabel>Diff Statistics</guilabel> dialog. The following "
"information is provided:"
msgstr ""
"Erinevuste kiireks ülevaateks vali menüükäsk <menuchoice><guimenu>Fail</"
"guimenu><guimenuitem>Näita statistikat</guimenuitem></menuchoice>. See avab "
"dialoogi <guilabel>Võrdlemise statistika</guilabel>. Selle näeb järgmist "
"teavet:"

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:244
#, no-c-format
msgid "Old file:"
msgstr "Vana fail:"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:245
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The file name of what is usually the source file or file that is unmodified."
msgstr "Tavaliselt lähtefaili või siis faili nimi, mida ei ole muudetud."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:248
#, no-c-format
msgid "New file:"
msgstr "Uus fail:"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:249
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The file name of what is usually the destination file or file that is "
"modified and to which differences will be applied."
msgstr ""
"Tavaliselt sihtfaili või siis faili nimi, mida on muudetud ja millele "
"erinevused rakendatakse."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:252
#, no-c-format
msgid "Format:"
msgstr "Vorming:"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:253
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The diff format used to display the difference (see <xref linkend=\"diff-"
"format\"/>)."
msgstr ""
"Erinevuste kuvamiseks kasutatud võrdlemisvorming (vt <xref linkend=\"diff-"
"format\"/>)."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:256
#, no-c-format
msgid "Number of hunks:"
msgstr "Tükke:"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:258
#, no-c-format
msgid "The number of hunks found in the difference."
msgstr "Võrdlemisel leitud tükkide arv."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:259
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"A hunk is a <quote>c<emphasis>hunk</emphasis></quote> of lines that have "
"been marked as different between source and destination and may include "
"context lines depending on the diff format <guilabel>Lines of Context</"
"guilabel> value (see <xref linkend=\"diff-format\"/>)."
msgstr ""
"Tükk (inglise keeles 'hunk', mis tuleneb sõnas <quote>c<emphasis>hunk</"
"emphasis></quote>) on ridade kogum, milles lähte- ja sihtfail erinevad; "
"nende hulka võivad kuuluda ka kontekstiread, kui võrdlemisvorminguks on "
"valitud <guilabel>Kontekst</guilabel> (vt. <xref linkend=\"diff-format\"/>)."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:263
#, no-c-format
msgid "Number of differences"
msgstr "Erinevusi"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:264
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The actual number of differences found, not hunks. A hunk can contain one or "
"more differences when the line change range and the context lines of any two "
"or more changes overlap."
msgstr ""
"Tegelike erinevuste, mitte tükkide arv. Tükk võib sisaldada rohkem kui üht "
"erinevust, kui kahe või enama muutuse read ja kontekstiread kattuvad."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:271
#, no-c-format
msgid "Navigating the Difference View"
msgstr "Liikumine erinevuste vaates"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:272
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&kompare; enables rapid navigation of differences on a file level and of "
"multiple difference files when comparing folder trees."
msgstr ""
"&kompare; võimaldab kiiret liikumist erinevuste vahel failide puhul ning "
"paljude erinevate failide vahel kataloogide puhul."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:275
#, no-c-format
msgid "Selecting a Difference"
msgstr "Erinevuse valimine"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:276
#, no-c-format
msgid "A difference can be selected using by:"
msgstr "Erinevust saab valida:"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:278
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"clicking a line in the Source and Destination Line Changes pane (top right "
"of the main window)."
msgstr ""
"klõpsuga reale lähte- ja sihtfaili ridade muutuste paneelil (peaaknas ülal "
"paremal)."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:279
#, no-c-format
msgid "clicking the highlighted difference in the View pane."
msgstr "klõpsuga esiletõstetud esinevusele vaatepaneelis."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:280
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"traversing the listed differences in a comparison (see <xref linkend="
"\"traversing-differences\"/>)."
msgstr ""
"toodud erinevusi võrdluses kõrvutades (vt. <xref linkend=\"traversing-"
"differences\"/>)."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:282
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"When a difference is selected it is considered to be <quote>in focus</quote> "
"and is displayed in a brighter color that non-selected differences."
msgstr ""
"Kui erinevus on valitud, satub see <quote>fookusse</quote> ning seda "
"kuvatakse mittevalitud erinevustega võrreldes heledama värviga."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:286
#, no-c-format
msgid "Traversing Differences"
msgstr "Erinevuste kõrvutamine"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:287
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"When a comparison finds many differences one of the best ways to approach "
"reviewing them is to traverse the differences in a logical order, usually "
"from top to bottom."
msgstr ""
"Kui võrdlemisel leitakse palju erinevusi, on neid kõige etem uurida "
"erinevusi loogilises järjekorras läbi vaadates, tavaliselt ülalt alla."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:288
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"By default &kompare; selects the first difference found in a comparison. By "
"selecting <menuchoice><guimenu>Difference</guimenu><guimenuitem>Next "
"Difference</guimenuitem></menuchoice> (<keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;"
"<keycap>Down</keycap></keycombo>) the difference following the current "
"selection is brought into focus. To select the difference before the current "
"difference select <menuchoice><guimenu>Difference</"
"guimenu><guimenuitem>Previous Difference</guimenuitem></menuchoice> "
"(<keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>Up</keycap></keycombo>)."
msgstr ""
"Vaikimisi valib &kompare; esimese võrdlemisel leitud erinevuse. Valides "
"menüükäsu <menuchoice><guimenu>Erinevus</guimenu><guimenuitem>Järgmine "
"erinevus</guimenuitem></menuchoice> (<keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;"
"<keycap>Nool alla</keycap></keycombo>), tuuakse fookusse aktiivsele valikule "
"järgnev erinevus. Aktiivsele valikule eelneva erinevuse nägemiseks vali "
"menüükäsk <menuchoice><guimenu>Erinevus</guimenu><guimenuitem>Eelmine "
"erinevus</guimenuitem></menuchoice> (<keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;"
"<keycap>Nool  üles</keycap></keycombo>)."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:294
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"In this way it is possible to traverse differences in an orderly manner, "
"applying and unapply differences upon review."
msgstr ""
"Sel moel saab erinevused kenasti läbi uurida ja neid rakendada või "
"rakendamata jätta."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:298
#, no-c-format
msgid "Switching Between Files"
msgstr "Lülitumine failide vahel"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:299
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"When a comparison is performed on folder level, many files may be found with "
"differences. A complete list of the files compared with difference found is "
"provided in the <quote>Source and Destination Folders</quote>, and "
"<quote>Source and Destination Files</quote> panes. However, &kompare; "
"displays differences between source and destination one comparison at time."
msgstr ""
"Kui võrrelda katalooge, siis võib leida palju erinevustega faile. Nende "
"täieliku nimekirja annavad paneelid <quote>Lähte- ja sihtkataloogid</quote> "
"ning <quote>Lähte- ja sihtfailid</quote>. Kuid &kompare; näitab korraga "
"ainult ühe lähte- ja sihtfaili erinevusi."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:302
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"To switch between documents in this scenario the following options are "
"available:"
msgstr "Dokumentide vahel saab sellisel juhul lülituda järgmiselt:"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:304
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Select the <quote>Source and Destination Folders</quote> pane to display "
"file differences found in the <quote>Source and Destination Files</quote> "
"pane, then select a file."
msgstr ""
"Vali <quote>Lähte- ja sihtkataloogide</quote> paneel, misjärel paneelil "
"<quote>Lähte- ja sihtfailid</quote> näeb erinevustega faile, mille seast "
"vali vajalik."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:306
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Select <menuchoice><guimenu>Difference</guimenu><guimenuitem>Previous File</"
"guimenuitem></menuchoice> (<keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>PgUp</"
"keycap></keycombo>) or <menuchoice><guimenu>Difference</"
"guimenu><guimenuitem>Next File</guimenuitem></menuchoice> (<keycombo action="
"\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>PgDown</keycap></keycombo>) to display the previous "
"or next difference file found in the <quote>Source and Destination Files</"
"quote> pane."
msgstr ""
"Vali menüükäsk <menuchoice><guimenu>Erinevus</guimenu><guimenuitem>Eelmine "
"fail</guimenuitem></menuchoice> (<keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;"
"<keycap>PgUp</keycap></keycombo>) või <menuchoice><guimenu>Erinevus</"
"guimenu><guimenuitem>Järgmine fail</guimenuitem></menuchoice>(<keycombo "
"action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>PgDown</keycap></keycombo>), et näha "
"vastavalt eelmis või järgmist erinevustega faili, mis on ära toodud paneelil "
"<quote>Lähte- ja sihtfailid</quote>."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:318
#, no-c-format
msgid "Merging Differences"
msgstr "Erinevuste ühendamine"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:320
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&kompare; makes the task of applying and unapplying differences as simple as "
"point and click. Multiple apply and unapply operations can be performed on a "
"difference as all operations are performed in memory and not written to the "
"files on disk until the save operation is performed."
msgstr ""
"&kompare; muudab erinevuste rakendamise või eemaldamise äärmiselt lihtsaks - "
"seda saab teha vaid hiireklõpsuga. Rakendamist võib sooritada korduvalt, "
"sest kõik toimingud sooritatakse mälus ja kirjutatakse kettale alles siis, "
"kui fail salvestatakse."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:324
#, no-c-format
msgid "Applying a Difference"
msgstr "Erinevuse rakendamine"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:325
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"To apply a difference, click the highlighted difference region, then select "
"<menuchoice><guimenu>Difference</guimenu><guimenuitem>Apply Difference</"
"guimenuitem></menuchoice> (<keycombo><keycap>Space</keycap></keycombo>)."
msgstr ""
"Erinevuse rakendamiseks klõpsa esiletõstetud erinevusele ja vali menüükäsk "
"<menuchoice><guimenu>Erinevus</guimenu><guimenuitem>Rakenda erinevus</"
"guimenuitem></menuchoice> (<keycombo><keycap>Tühikuklahv</keycap></"
"keycombo>)."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:330
#, no-c-format
msgid "Unapplying a Difference"
msgstr "Erinevuse eemaldamine"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:331
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"To unapply a difference, click the highlighted difference region previously "
"applied, then select <menuchoice><guimenu>Difference</"
"guimenu><guimenuitem>Unapply Difference</guimenuitem></menuchoice> "
"(<keycombo>&Backspace;</keycombo>)."
msgstr ""
"Erinevuse eemaldamiseks klõpsa esiletõstetud erinevusel, mille varem "
"rakendasid, ja vali menüükäsk <menuchoice><guimenu>Erinevus</"
"guimenu><guimenuitem>Eemalda erinevus</guimenuitem></menuchoice> "
"(<keycombo>&Backspace;</keycombo>)."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:336
#, no-c-format
msgid "Applying All Differences"
msgstr "Kõigi erinevuste rakendamine"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:337
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"After reviewing differences between files and finding all acceptable it is "
"possible apply them all with a single operation by selecting "
"<menuchoice><guimenu>Difference</guimenu><guimenuitem>Apply All</"
"guimenuitem></menuchoice> (<keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>A</"
"keycap></keycombo>)."
msgstr ""
"Kui oled kõik failide erinevused läbi vaadanud ja arvad, et neid võiks kõiki "
"rakendada, vali menüükäsk <menuchoice><guimenu>Erinevus</"
"guimenu><guimenuitem>Rakenda kõik</guimenuitem></menuchoice> (<keycombo "
"action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>A</keycap></keycombo>)."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:342
#, no-c-format
msgid "Unapplying All Differences"
msgstr "Kõigi erinevuste eemaldamine"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:343
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"To revert all differences that have been applied previously select "
"<menuchoice><guimenu>Difference</guimenu><guimenuitem>Unapply All</"
"guimenuitem></menuchoice> (<keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>U</"
"keycap></keycombo>)."
msgstr ""
"Kui soovid kõik rakendatud erinevused eemaldada, vali "
"<menuchoice><guimenu>Erinevus</guimenu><guimenuitem>Eemalda rakendus "
"kõigilt</guimenuitem></menuchoice> (<keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;"
"<keycap>U</keycap></keycombo>)."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:348
#, no-c-format
msgid "Saving Changes"
msgstr "Muudatuste salvestamine"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:349
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Once differences have been applied they can be saved by selecting "
"<menuchoice><guimenu>File</guimenu><guimenuitem>Save</guimenuitem></"
"menuchoice> or <menuchoice><guimenu>File</guimenu><guimenuitem>Save All</"
"guimenuitem></menuchoice>."
msgstr ""
"Kui erinevused on rakendatud, oleks mõttekas need salvestada menüükäsuga "
"<menuchoice><guimenu>Fail</guimenu><guimenuitem>Salvesta</guimenuitem></"
"menuchoice> või <menuchoice><guimenu>Fail</guimenu><guimenuitem>Salvesta "
"kõik</guimenuitem></menuchoice>."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:352
#, no-c-format
msgid "Applied differences are saved to both the source and destination file."
msgstr "Rakendatud erinevused salvestatakse nii lähte- kui ka sihtfaili."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:357
#, no-c-format
msgid "Working with Diff Files"
msgstr "Erinevusfailide kasutamine"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:358
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Diff files contain only the changes made between files, or a set of files "
"within a folder system, and may or may not contain a number of context lines "
"before and after line changes. The sum of a line change and its context "
"lines is known a hunk. A diff file therefore may contain multiple hunks from "
"one or more files. When the context lines of two or more hunks overlap, they "
"are considered a single hunk. Diff files can be used to:"
msgstr ""
"Erinevusfailid (diff-failid) sisaldavad ainult failide erinevusi ning võivad "
"sisaldada ka teatud hulka kontekstiridasid enne ja pärast erinevaid ridu. "
"Muudetud ridade ja selle kontekstiridade kogumit nimetatakse tükiks. "
"Võrdlusfail võib niisiis sisaldada mitut tükki ühest või enamast failist. "
"Kui kahe või enama tüki kontekstiread kattuvad, peetakse neid üheks tükiks. "
"Erinevusfaile saab kasutada järgmisteks ülesanneteks:"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:362
#, no-c-format
msgid "Apply the changes contained in the hunks to an original file."
msgstr "Tükkides sisalduvate muudatuste rakendamiseks originaalfailile."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:363
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Apply the changes contained in the hunks to a file or set of original files "
"within a folder system."
msgstr ""
"Tükkides sisalduvate muudatuste rakendamiseks originaalfailile või "
"failikogumile."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:364
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Modified before being applied to an original file or set of original files "
"within a folder system."
msgstr "Muutmiseks enne rakendamist originaalfailile või failikogumile."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:368
#, no-c-format
msgid "Creating a Diff"
msgstr "Erinevusfaili loomine"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:369
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"To create a diff file a comparison must be displayed in &kompare;. Assuming "
"this is the case, then select <menuchoice><guimenu>File</"
"guimenu><guimenuitem>Save Diff...</guimenuitem></menuchoice> This will "
"display the <guilabel>Diff Options</guilabel> dialog (see <xref linkend="
"\"diff-settings\"/> for more information on diff formats and options). After "
"configuring these options, click the <guibutton>Save</guibutton> button and "
"save the diff to a file with the extension <filename class=\"extension\">."
"diff</filename>."
msgstr ""
"Erinevusfaili loomiseks tuleb võrdlust &kompare;s kuvada. Seejärel vali "
"menüükäsk <menuchoice><guimenu>Fail</guimenu><guimenuitem>Salvesta diff...</"
"guimenuitem></menuchoice> See avab dialoogi <guilabel>Diffi valikud</"
"guilabel> (täpsemalt kõneleb diffi vormingutest ja valikutest <xref linkend="
"\"diff-settings\"/>). Pärast valikute määramist klõpsa nupule "
"<guibutton>Salvesta</guibutton> ning salvesta erinevused faili laiendiga "
"<filename class=\"extension\">.diff</filename>."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:375
#, no-c-format
msgid "Displaying a Diff"
msgstr "Erinevusfaili vaatamine"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:376
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"It is possible to display the contents of a diff file within &kompare; by "
"opening the diff file from <menuchoice><guimenu>File</"
"guimenu><guimenuitem>Open Diff...</guimenuitem></menuchoice>."
msgstr ""
"Diff-faili on võimalik &kompare;s ka vaadata, kui see avada "
"menüükäsuga<menuchoice><guimenu>Fail</guimenu><guimenuitem>Ava diff...</"
"guimenuitem></menuchoice>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:377
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"When viewing a diff file the hunks between the source and destination file "
"are shown, remember that only the hunks are shown, no unmodified lines will "
"be shown. In some cases a diff file is created with 0 lines of context. In "
"this case only the changed lines will be displayed."
msgstr ""
"Diff-faili kuvamisel näidatakse lähte ja sihtfaili tükke. Pea meeles, et "
"näidatakse ainult tükke, mitte aga muutusteta ridu. Mõnel juhul luuakse diff-"
"fail üldse ilma kontekstiridadeta. Sel juhul on näha ainult muudetud read."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:379
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"When a diff file contains hunks from multiple files &kompare; displays the "
"hunks from each file one at a time and you can switch between files as "
"though they were real files even though this information is only provided by "
"the diff file contents."
msgstr ""
"Kui diff-fail sisaldab tükke mitmest failist, näitab &kompare; korraga "
"ainult ühe faili tükke ning sa saad failide vahel liikuda, nagu oleksid nad "
"tegelikud failid, ehkki nende info pärineb kõigest diff-faili sisust."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:384
#, no-c-format
msgid "Applying Differences in a Diff File"
msgstr "Diff-faili erinevuste rakendamine"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:385
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"When viewing differences in a diff file it is possible to apply difference "
"as you would when comparing source and destination files (see <xref linkend="
"\"merging-differences\"/>)."
msgstr ""
"Diff-faili erinevusi vaadates saab neid rakendada samamoodi, nagu lähte- ja "
"sihtfaili võrdlemisel (vt. <xref linkend=\"merging-differences\"/>)."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:389
#, no-c-format
msgid "Blending a &URL; with a Diff"
msgstr "&URL;-i ühendamine diff'iga"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:390
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"In cases where a diff file is provided it is possible to compare the hunks "
"in the diff against a file or folder. To do this select "
"<menuchoice><guimenu>File</guimenu><guimenuitem>Blend URL with Diff...</"
"guimenuitem></menuchoice>. Then input the <guilabel>File/Folder</guilabel> "
"and <guilabel>Diff Output</guilabel> paths."
msgstr ""
"Diff-faili korral on võimalik võrrelda selle tükke faili või kataloogiga. "
"Selleks vali menüükäsk <menuchoice><guimenu>Fail</guimenu><guimenuitem>Liida "
"URL diffiga</guimenuitem></menuchoice>. Seejärel anna <guilabel>faili/"
"kataloogi</guilabel> ja <guilabel>diffi väljundi</guilabel> asukohad."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:393
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"When viewing differences between a source file and a diff file it is "
"possible to apply difference as you would when comparing source and "
"destination files (see <xref linkend=\"merging-differences\"/>)."
msgstr ""
"Lähtefaili ja diff-faili erinevusi vaadates võib neid rakendada samamoodi, "
"nagu lähte- ja sihtfaili võrdlemisel (vt. <xref linkend=\"merging-differences"
"\"/>)."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:400
#, no-c-format
msgid "Configuring Preferences"
msgstr "Seadistamine"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:402
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&kompare; enables users to set appearance preferences for difference "
"formatting in the main interface and set behavioral properties of the diff "
"program. The <guilabel>Preferences</guilabel> dialog can be accessed by "
"selecting <menuchoice><guimenu>Settings</guimenu><guisubmenu>Configure "
"&kompare;...</guisubmenu></menuchoice>."
msgstr ""
"&kompare; lubab kasutajatel määrata erinevuste vormindust peaaknas ning "
"muuta programmi diff käitumist. Dialoogi <guilabel>Seadistused</guilabel> "
"avamiseks vali <menuchoice><guimenu>Seadistused</"
"guimenu><guisubmenu>&kompare; seadistamine...</guisubmenu></menuchoice>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:406
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"To configure preferences for appearance select the <guilabel>View</guilabel> "
"menu item (see <xref linkend=\"view-settings\"/>)."
msgstr ""
"Välimuse seadistamiseks vali kaart <guilabel>Vaade</guilabel> (vt. <xref "
"linkend=\"view-settings\"/>)."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:408
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"To configure preferences for diff program properties select the "
"<guilabel>Diff</guilabel> menu item (see <xref linkend=\"diff-settings\"/>)."
msgstr ""
"Programmi diff omaduste seadistamiseks vali kaart <guilabel> Diff</guilabel> "
"(<xref linkend=\"diff-settings\"/>)."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:411
#, no-c-format
msgid "View Settings"
msgstr "Vaateseadistused"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:412
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The <guimenu>View</guimenu> page in the <guilabel>Preferences</guilabel> "
"dialog displays the <guilabel>Appearance</guilabel> and <guilabel>Fonts</"
"guilabel> tabbed forms."
msgstr ""
"Dialoogi <guilabel>Seadistused</guilabel> kaardil <guimenu>Vaade</guimenu>on "
"kaks alamkaarti: <guilabel>Välimus</guilabel> ja <guilabel>Fondid</guilabel>."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:416
#, no-c-format
msgid "Appearance"
msgstr "Välimus"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:417
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The <guilabel>Appearance</guilabel> form provides controls to manage the "
"<guilabel>Colors</guilabel> used to denote difference in the main interface, "
"behavior of the <guilabel>Mouse Wheel</guilabel> when jogging up and down "
"and how <guilabel>Tabs to Spaces</guilabel> conversion is managed."
msgstr ""
"Kaart <guilabel>Välimus</guilabel> võimaldab määrata <guilabel>värve</"
"guilabel>, mida kasutatakse erinevuste tähistamisel peaaknas, "
"<guilabel>hiireratta</guilabel> käitumist kerimisel ning seda, kuidas muuta "
"<guilabel>tabeldusmärgid tühikuteks</guilabel>."

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: index.docbook:421
#, no-c-format
msgid "<screeninfo>&kompare; Appearance Settings</screeninfo>"
msgstr "<screeninfo>&kompare; välimuse seadistused</screeninfo>"

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:427
#, no-c-format
msgid "<phrase>&kompare; Appearance Settings</phrase>"
msgstr "<phrase>&kompare; välimuse seadistused</phrase>"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:432
#, no-c-format
msgid "Color Group"
msgstr "Värvisektsioon"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:433
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"To adjust color preferences used when displaying differences, click the "
"color button to display the <guilabel>Select Color</guilabel> dialog for the "
"following states:"
msgstr ""
"Erinevuste kuvamisel kasutatavate värvide muutmiseks klõpsa "
"<guilabel>värvide valimise</guilabel> sektsioonis värvinuppudele. Muuta saab "
"järgmisi värve:"

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:435
#, no-c-format
msgid "Removed color"
msgstr "Eemaldamise värv"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:436
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Lines that have been removed, do not exist, between source and destination."
msgstr "Read, mis on eemaldatud ja mida enam ei ole."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:439
#, no-c-format
msgid "Changed color"
msgstr "Muutmise värv"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:440
#, no-c-format
msgid "Lines that have been changed, modified, between source and destination."
msgstr "Read, mis on muudetud."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:443
#, no-c-format
msgid "Added color"
msgstr "Lisamise värv"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:444
#, no-c-format
msgid "Lines that have been added between source and destination."
msgstr "Read, mis on lisatud."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:447
#, no-c-format
msgid "Applied color"
msgstr "Rakendamise värv"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:448
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Any of the above states where the difference has been applied between source "
"and destination."
msgstr "Mis tahes eelnevalt toodud olek, mille korral erinevus on rakendatud."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:452
#, no-c-format
msgid "Mouse Wheel"
msgstr "Hiireratas"

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:454
#, no-c-format
msgid "Number of lines"
msgstr "Ridade arv"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:455
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The number of lines to jog the differences when turning the mouse wheel "
"forward or backward."
msgstr "Ridade arv, mille võrra hiireratas kerib."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:459
#, no-c-format
msgid "Tabs to Spaces"
msgstr "Tabeldusmärgid tühikuteks"

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:461
#, no-c-format
msgid "Number of spaces to convert a tab character to"
msgstr "Tabeldusmärgi asendamisel lisatakse tühikuid"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:462
#, no-c-format
msgid "Convert each tab character to n space characters."
msgstr "Tühikute arv, millega tabeldusmärgid asendatakse."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:468
#, no-c-format
msgid "Fonts"
msgstr "Fondid"

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: index.docbook:470
#, no-c-format
msgid "<screeninfo>&kompare; Fonts Settings</screeninfo>"
msgstr "<screeninfo>&kompare; fondiseadistused</screeninfo>"

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:476
#, no-c-format
msgid "<phrase>&kompare; Fonts Settings</phrase>"
msgstr "<phrase>&kompare; fondiseadistused</phrase>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:480
#, no-c-format
msgid "Select the font family and size to display when displaying differences."
msgstr "Siin saab valida fondipere ja -suuruse, millega erinevusi kuvatakse."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:485
#, no-c-format
msgid "Diff Settings"
msgstr "Võrdlemise seadistused"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:486
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The <guimenu>Diff</guimenu> page in the <guilabel>Preferences</guilabel> "
"dialog displays the <guilabel>Diff</guilabel>, <guilabel>Format</guilabel>, "
"<guilabel>Options</guilabel> and <guilabel>Exclude</guilabel> tabbed forms. "
"These forms can be used to configure the behavioral properties of the Diff "
"program."
msgstr ""
"Dialoogi <guilabel>Seadistused</guilabel> kaardil <guimenu>Diff</guimenu> on "
"järgmised alamkaardid: <guilabel>Diff</guilabel>, <guilabel>Vorming</"
"guilabel>, <guilabel>Valikud</guilabel> ja <guilabel>Väljajätmine</"
"guilabel>. Nende abil saab seadistada programmi diff käitumist."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:491
#, no-c-format
msgid "<title>Diff</title>"
msgstr "<title>Diff</title>"

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: index.docbook:493
#, no-c-format
msgid "<screeninfo>&kompare; Diff Settings</screeninfo>"
msgstr "<screeninfo>&kompare; diffi seadistused</screeninfo>"

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:499
#, no-c-format
msgid "<phrase>&kompare; Diff Settings</phrase>"
msgstr "<phrase>&kompare; diffi seadistused</phrase>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:503
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The command used to run the diff program (default <application>diff</"
"application>)."
msgstr ""
"Programmi diff käivitamiseks antav käsk (vaikimisi <application>diff</"
"application>)."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:507
#, no-c-format
msgid "Format"
msgstr "Vorming"

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: index.docbook:509
#, no-c-format
msgid "<screeninfo>&kompare; Format Settings</screeninfo>"
msgstr "<screeninfo>&kompare; vorminguseadistused</screeninfo>"

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:515
#, no-c-format
msgid "<phrase>&kompare; Format Settings</phrase>"
msgstr "<phrase>&kompare; vorminguseadistused</phrase>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:519
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Adjust options for the <guilabel>Output Format</guilabel> and number of "
"<guilabel>Lines of Context</guilabel>."
msgstr ""
"Siin saab kohandada  <guilabel>väljundvormingu</guilabel> omadusi ja "
"<guilabel>kontekstiridade</guilabel> arvu."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:521
#, no-c-format
msgid "Output Format"
msgstr "Väljundvorming"

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:523
#, no-c-format
msgid "Context"
msgstr "Kontekst"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:525
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The context output format adds several lines of context around the lines "
"that differ."
msgstr ""
"Kontekstiväljundi korral lisatakse erinevusi sisaldavate ridade ümber mõned "
"kontekstiread."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:530
#, no-c-format
msgid "Normal"
msgstr "Tavaline"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:532
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The normal output format displays differing lines without any surrounding "
"lines of context."
msgstr ""
"Tavaline väljundvorming näitab erinevusi sisaldavaid ridu ilma "
"kontekstiridadeta."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:537
#, no-c-format
msgid "Unified"
msgstr "Unifitseeritud"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:539
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The unified output format is a variation on the context format. It is "
"considered better than context because the output is more compact than that "
"of context as it omits redundant context lines."
msgstr ""
"Unifitseeritud väljundvorming on kontekstivormingu erim. Seda peetakse "
"mõnevõrra paremaks, sest väljund on üleliigsete kontekstiridade väljajätmise "
"tõttu märksa kompaktsem."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:546
#, no-c-format
msgid "Lines of Context"
msgstr "Kontekstiread"

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:548
#, no-c-format
msgid "Number of context lines"
msgstr "Kontekstiridade arv"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:550
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"When performing a diff with context or unified output format use this "
"parameter to control the number of context lines included."
msgstr ""
"Konteksti või unifitseeritud väljundvormingu valimisel saab siin määrata, "
"mitu kontekstirida väljundisse kaasatakse."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:557
#, no-c-format
msgid "Options"
msgstr "Valikud"

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: index.docbook:559
#, no-c-format
msgid "<screeninfo>&kompare; Options Settings</screeninfo>"
msgstr "<screeninfo>&kompare; valikute seadistused</screeninfo>"

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:565
#, no-c-format
msgid "<phrase>&kompare; Options Settings</phrase>"
msgstr "<phrase>&kompare; valikute seadistused</phrase>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:569
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The <guilabel>Options</guilabel> tab form allows configuration of the "
"options supported by the diff program."
msgstr ""
"Kaardil <guilabel>Valikud</guilabel> saab seadistada programmi diff valikuid."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:571
#, no-c-format
msgid "General"
msgstr "Üldine"

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:573
#, no-c-format
msgid "Treat new files as empty"
msgstr "Uusi faile koheldakse tühjana"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:574
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"With this option enabled diff will treat a file that only exists in one of "
"the directories as empty in the other directory. This means that the file is "
"compared with an empty file and because of this will appear as one big "
"insertion or deletion."
msgstr ""
"Sisselülitamisel koheldakse ainult ühes kataloogis leiduvat faili "
"võrdlemisel teises kataloogis tühja failina. See tähendab, et faili "
"võrreldakse tühja failiga ning seetõttu on näha vaid üks suur lisamine või "
"kustutamine."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:580
#, no-c-format
msgid "Look for smaller changes"
msgstr "Otsitakse väiksemaid muudatusi"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:581
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Forces diff to display changes in case, punctuation, space, &etc; when "
"checked."
msgstr ""
"Märkimisel kuvab diff ka muudatusi tähesuuruses, kirjavahemärkides, "
"tühikutes &etc;"

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:584
#, no-c-format
msgid "Optimize for large files"
msgstr "Optimeeritakse suurte failide jaoks"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:585
#, no-c-format
msgid "Switches diff to process files with high-speed when checked."
msgstr "Märkimisel töötleb diff faile äärmise kiirusega."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:588
#, no-c-format
msgid "Ignore changes in case"
msgstr "Ignoreeritakse suur- ja väiketähe muudatusi"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:589
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Lower and Uppercase character changes are omitted when this option is "
"checked."
msgstr "Märkimisel ei arvestata väike- ja suurtähe erinevustega."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:594
#, no-c-format
msgid "Ignore regexp"
msgstr "Ignoreeritakse regulaaravaldist"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:595
#, no-c-format
msgid "Ignore lines matching a regular expression."
msgstr "Ignoreeritakse määratud regulaaravaldisega ridu."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:599
#, no-c-format
msgid "Whitespace"
msgstr "Tühimärk"

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:601
#, no-c-format
msgid "Expand tabs to spaces in output"
msgstr "Tabeldusmärgid muudetakse väljundis tühikuteks"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:602
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"When checked diff outputs will converts tab characters to the number of "
"spaces defined in the <guilabel>Preferences</guilabel> dialog <guimenu>View</"
"guimenu> menu <guilabel>Tabs to Spaces</guilabel> option."
msgstr ""
"Märkimisel muudetakse diffi väljundis tabeldusmärgid tühikuteks, mille arv "
"on määratud dialoogi <guilabel>Seadistused</guilabel> kaardil "
"<guimenu>Vaade</guimenu> valikuga <guilabel>Tabeldusmärgid tühikuteks</"
"guilabel>."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:607
#, no-c-format
msgid "Ignore added or removed empty lines"
msgstr "Ignoreeritakse lisatud või eemaldatud tühje ridu"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:608
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"lines of zero length that differ between source and destination are ignored "
"when this option is checked."
msgstr "Märkimisel eiratakse null märgi pikkuste ridade erinevusi."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:611
#, no-c-format
msgid "Ignore changes in the amount of whitespace"
msgstr "Ingoreeritakse muutusi tühimärkide arvus"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:612
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"White space before, after and between lines may change depending on "
"different editors. When this option is checked such changes are ignored."
msgstr ""
"Erinevates redaktorites võib tühimärkide arv enne ja pärast ridu ning nende "
"vahel olla erinev. Märkimisel selliseid erinevusi eiratakse."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:616
#, no-c-format
msgid "Ignore all whitespace"
msgstr "Ignoreeritakse kõiki tühimärke"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:617
#, no-c-format
msgid "when checked white space differences are completely ignored."
msgstr "Märkimisel eiratakse täielikult tühimärkide erinevusi."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:620
#, no-c-format
msgid "Ignore changes due to tab expansion"
msgstr "Ignoreeritakse tabeldusmärkide muutmisest tulenevaid muudatusi"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:621
#, no-c-format
